### 4. Continuous Deployment Ready ([app/upload/page.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/upload/page.tsx))
The upload workflow now triggers the transcoding pipeline automatically.
- Users see more detailed progress states ("Optimizing for adaptive streaming...").
- Fallback logic ensures that if transcoding fails, the raw video is still preserved to prevent data loss.

## Background Uploads & Global State
I implemented a [UploadProvider](file:///C:/GOLive/components/UploadProvider.tsx#33-243) context that enables true background processing. Users can now initiate an upload and immediately navigate to other parts of the platform while the progress is tracked via a global toast notification.

